item.description: About Us GL Natural Healthcare GL Natural Healthcare Clinic has been providing service of acupuncture and Chinese herbal medicine to people in Northern suburbs for many years. It has been successfully operated by Dr George Lenon who incorporated his academic and research into his practice. His reputation spreads over Melbourne, with patients regularly travelling from as far as Bendigo, Ballarat and Rosebud etc. Now GL Natural Healthcare extends to Docklands to provide services to docklands residents and workers.
